	<h1 class="title">《激战》火了后，林超贤拍了他当导演以来最贵的电影</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">刘平安 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-23 17:44:18 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/10801/medium/10801.jpg?1436645526" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="10801" data-title="《《激战》火了后，林超贤拍了他当导演以来最贵的电影》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/10801/medium/10801.jpg?1436645526" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/10801.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
